headline: Vulcan Materials’s (NYSE:VMC) Q3: Beats On Revenue
summary: Construction materials company Vulcan Materials (NYSE:VMC) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 14.4% year on year to $2.29 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.84 per share was 4.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Vulcan: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
